on. All users who are apprehensive about upgrading their website are endangering their security and putting confidential information of users at risk.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Here_are_top_hacks_and_industry_best_practices_for_WordPress_Developers\"><\/span>Here are top hacks and industry best practices for WordPress Developers<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3 style=\"color: #000; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 40px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Limit_login_attempts\"><\/span>Limit login attempts<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Security is one of the major woes for WordPress sites. By default, WordPress does not put a cap on login attempts. This allows anyone to try guessing passwords until they get it right. In order to control this menace, it is important to install plugin that allows setting limits on the number of failed attempts a user can make to login.<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"color: #000; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 40px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Adding_Custom_CSS_to_a_WordPress_Theme\"><\/span>Adding Custom CSS to a WordPress Theme<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>WordPress site owners may need to add custom CSS to your site, allowing changing the appearance of things on your WordPress site like colors, margins, and font sizes. The simplest method to add custom CSS to any WordPress theme is by visiting the Appearance \u00bb Customize page in your WordPress admin. This will help launch the WordPress theme customizer and you will observe your website\u2019s preview in the right panel.<\/p>\n<p>Immediately click on the \u2018Additional CSS\u2019 menu in the left panel to expand it. You will notice a plain text box to add your custom CSS. Immediately, you add a valid CSS rule and see it applied on your website\u2019s live preview pane.<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"color: #000; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 40px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Sticky_Floating_Navigation_Menu\"><\/span>Sticky Floating Navigation Menu<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Sticky floating navigation menu comes at the top of the screen as and when a user scrolls down. Select few WordPress themes have this feature as an option in settings. In case you have a theme without this option, then you can try this method. First step would involve, installation and activation of the plugin.<\/p>\n<p>Upon activation, go to the plugin&#8217;s settings page located under Settings \u00bb Sticky Menu. Add the CSS class of your navigation menu and save changes.<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"color: #000; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 40px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Remove_WordPress_Version_Number\"><\/span>Remove WordPress Version Number<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>WordPress adds the version in your website\u2019s header. However, some consider it as a security liability. While the simple solution is to keep WordPress updated. In case, you want to remove the WordPress version number, just add given code to theme\u2019s functions.php file or a site-specific plugin.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Top_WordPress_Plugins\"><\/span>Top WordPress Plugins<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3 style=\"color: #000; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 40px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"OptinMonster\"><\/span>OptinMonster<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>OptinMonster is one of the most powerful lead generation software for marketing agencies, bloggers, eCommerce websites, and small businesses. If you want your email list to expand, augment your website conversions, and decrease cart abandonment, then OptinMonster is the best option. With drag and drop campaign builder, OptinMonster makes it super easy to create beautiful, effective, high-converting options that are mobile-friendly.<\/p>\n<ul style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">\n<li>Integrated A\/B Testing<\/li>\n<li>Device Targeting<\/li>\n<li>Page Level Targeting<\/li>\n<li>Geolocation Targeting<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 style=\"color: #000; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 40px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Sucuri\"><\/span>Sucuri<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Sucuri provides an option to clean and protect websites, giving a complete peace of mind by securing all your websites. The focus is towards fixing hacks and preventing possible future attacks. Right from restoring the site completely to removing any malicious code in your website file system and database, Sucuri is the key to safety.<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Submit blacklist removal requests on your behalf.<\/li>\n<li>Repair SEO Spam that can cripple your brand in terms of value. Ensure your website appears right in search engines.<\/li>\n<li>Website firewall (WAF) blocks attacks by providing filters to malicious traffic, as well as stopping hackers from ruining the speed up your site.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 style=\"color: #000; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 40px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"All_In_One_WP_Security_Firewall\"><\/span>All In One WP Security &amp; Firewall<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>While WordPress is taking security very seriously, All in One WP Security &amp; Firewall helps to instill extra security measures and firewall to your site by using a security plugin that enforces industry best security practices. The All In One WordPress Security plugin will take your website security to a whole new level. Written and designed by experts, it is easy to use and understand.<\/p>\n<p>It minimizes security risk by assessing vulnerabilities, and by implementing and enforcing the latest recommended WordPress security practices and techniques.<\/p>\n<ul style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">\n<li>Login Lockdown keeps your WordPress site protected against brute force attacks<\/li>\n<li>Force logout capabilities<\/li>\n<li>Blacklist specific IPs or IP ranges<\/li>\n<li>Security dashboard that shows important info like failed login attempts, account activity, and users online<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 style=\"color: #000; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 40px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"UpdraftPlus\"><\/span>UpdraftPlus<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>UpdraftPlus is a trusted WordPress backup, restore and clone plugin. Whether it is hacking, server crashes, shady updates or simple user error can ruin your WordPress site. It keeps your WordPress site safe and installed now. UpdraftPlus conducts complete manual or scheduled backups of each WordPress files, databases, plugins and themes.<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Offers the flexibility to set Backup schedules every 4, 8 or 12 hours, daily, weekly, fortnightly or monthly.<\/li>\n<li>Restore backups directly from your WordPress control panel.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 style=\"color: #000; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 40px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Yoast\"><\/span>Yoast<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Nearly 20,000+ WordPress users can\u2019t all make an error? That\u2019s the number of user people have given the Yoast SEO plugin a 5-Star review in the WordPress plugin repository. With 5 million WordPress users installing on the websites, Yoast SEO does it all. If people can\u2019t find you in search results, they can\u2019t buy from you, right? Search Engine Optimization (SEO) helps you connect with the people who are looking for your products and services.<\/p>\n<p>Yoast SEO helps you with brand awareness, site traffic, social media, pay-per-click ads (PPC), lead generation, and simply about everything that you need to keep your business growing.<\/p>\n<h4 style=\"font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 42px; color: #0a57f4;\">Conclusion<\/h4>\n<p>We hope this blog provides you interesting hacks and tools th